{"tid":2207444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[中國或成最大贏家] 逾1700間日本企業撤出中國，較日本政府預算高出11倍","createTime":"2020-09-18T07:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T07:25:02.000Z","uid":12746,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01cfe980a56a1b7ccb2e0aa2fef42b780b99a1c5","tid":2207444,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"日本政府早前決定出資幫助日本企業撤離中國，構築更為安全穩健的產業鍊。據《日本經濟新聞》報導，目前已有1670間在中國設廠的日本公司申請補助，申請金額比起政府規劃的預算高出11倍之多。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府早前因應新冠疫情突顯「產業供應鏈的脆弱性」與「生產基地過於集中」的問題，為確保產品與材料的順利供應，因此在2020財年的追加預算動用其中2200億日圓，協助日本企業撤回日本。不過首輪（今年7月）僅有90間企業申請的這項補助，第二輪卻湧入了1670間在華日本企業申請，如果全部獲得補助，補助金額將上看1.76兆日幣，是預算金額的11倍之多。<br />\n<br />\n《日經》指出，由於勞動成本上升，在中國設廠的吸引力早已大不如前，加上中美之間的新冷戰，讓不少<span class=\"red\">日本企業「就算沒有補助也要離開中國」</span>。據報，目前第二輪申請已經截止，10月份將由外部專家審查後選出第二輪補助名單。由於太多日本公司想要撤走，<span class=\"red\">《日經》甚至形容「日本企業正在排隊離開中國」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BusinessDigest.io/posts/799848190826835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBusinessDigest.io%2Fposts%2F799848190826835&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=ede4f5a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BusinessDigest.io/posts/799848190826835</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/article/商業熱話/4981/日資撤離-日媒-逾1700間日本企業申請資助撤出中國-較日本政府預算高出11倍\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Farticle%2F%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F4981%2F%E6%97%A5%E8%B3%87%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2-%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E9%80%BE1700%E9%96%93%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E8%BC%83%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E9%AB%98%E5%87%BA11%E5%80%8D&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=9405d36b\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/article/商業熱話/4981/日資撤離-日媒-逾1700間日本企業申請資助撤出中國-較日本政府預算高出11倍</a>"},{"pid":"1e4b162d786678b629e59284f47a2b582476e830","tid":2207444,"uid":12746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/24/Tvb_hail_commie_winner.png/revision/latest?cb=20181215123622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F24%2FTvb_hail_commie_winner.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20181215123622&h=9521c68c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f12003ac2d88284ff3c3098fffbf2b6cbac6132","tid":2207444,"uid":12746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/235155_de2fdd8e3afd415f264507055d924446.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F235155_de2fdd8e3afd415f264507055d924446.gif&h=c8483b58&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}